            </div>
            <div class="about__image"><img src="images/Home/Home-About-now.jpg" alt="About Us" /></div>
            <div class="about__content animate-page-content">
              <!-- Desktop-only title below image -->
              <div class="about__desktop-title page-header animate-page-header">
                <h2 class="page-header__title">
                  <span class="decrypt-text wave-text wave-ripple" data-text="Bits & Pieces About Me" tabindex="0" aria-label="Bits & Pieces About Me" role="button">Bits & Pieces About Me</span>
                </h2>
              </div>
              <div class="about__text">
                <p>
                  I'm a systems-driven <strong>Software Engineer</strong>,<strong>Data Scientist</strong> and <strong>Consultant </strong> who builds <strong>AI-first solutions</strong> at the intersection of <strong>healthcare</strong>, <strong>neuroscience</strong>, and <strong>business automation</strong>.<br>
                  As an <strong>NIH-funded researcher</strong>, I've architected pipelines processing <strong>30TB+</strong> of neuroimaging data and led wearable studies with <strong>100+ Apple Watches</strong> to decode human learning and performance.<br>
                  Most recently, I engineered a <strong>financial automation stack</strong> that reduced manual workflows from hours to seconds, driving <strong>$1M+</strong> in daily deal flows.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Modal trigger buttons container -->
              <div class="about__buttons">
                <button id="open-modal" class="about__toggle-button btn" type="button">
                  + More details
                </button>
                <button id="open-education-modal" class="about__toggle-button btn" type="button">
                  + Education
                </button>
                <button id="open-toolbox-modal" class="about__toggle-button btn" type="button">
                  + Toolbox
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Technical Details Modal -->
        <div id="technical-modal" class="modal" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="modal-title" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="modal__backdrop"></div>
          <div class="modal__container">
            <div class="modal__header">
              <h2 id="modal-title" class="modal__title">
                <span class="decrypt-text wave-text" data-text="Technical Deep Dive" tabindex="0">Technical Deep Dive</span>
              </h2>
              <button id="close-modal" class="modal__close" type="button" aria-label="Close modal">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal__content">
              <div class="modal__text">
                <p>
                  I'm a systems-driven <strong>Software Engineer</strong> and <strong>Data Scientist</strong> with roots in <strong>neuroscience</strong> and a track record of building <strong>AI-first pipelines</strong> across healthcare, brain research, and financial automation. As an <strong>NIH-funded researcher</strong>, I've led multi-year neuroimaging studies across Emory, the NIH, and the VA, developing terminal-native pipelines for over <strong>30TB of fMRI, MRS, and TMS data</strong> to decode aging, neuroplasticity, and GABA modulation during task learning.
                </p>
                <p>
                  I architected <strong>wearable-integrated studies</strong> involving <strong>100+ Apple Watches</strong> to correlate cardiovascular dynamics with real-time metabolic neurochemistry, bridging physiological telemetry with spectroscopic brain signals for novel insights into human learning and performance.
                </p>
                <p>
                  In <strong>digital pathology</strong>, I digitized <strong>100,000+ paraffin-embedded tissue blocks</strong> and built a secure, cloud-ready archival system using Leica Cerebro and SQL-powered access controls. I onboarded hundreds of researchers across hospital, academic, and compliance boundaries.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Most recently, I served as the sole engineer behind a <strong>financial automation stack</strong> that unified lead generation, ETL, NLP classification, and PowerBI dashboards. This reduced manual workflows from hours to seconds and drove <strong>$1M per day in deal flows</strong>.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Whether processing brainwaves, tissue slides, or business logic, I build <strong>real-time, reproducible systems that scale</strong>. I turn raw data into decisions, and decisions into momentum for teams tackling the world's most complex problems.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Education Modal -->
